Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.abilities

Class DefaultAbilities

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.abilities.DefaultAbilities
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAbilities
public class DefaultAbilities
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAbilities
The class representing the abilities of a player that hasn't got any god effect. This class is used in a simple game.
